　FIG. 1 depicts an exemplary LED lighting apparatus
		including a primary LED lighting device and secondary LED lighting device(s)
		consistent with various disclosed embodiments;

claim.claim-text:
the primary LED lighting device includes a WiFi module and a
		  Zigbee module, the WiFi module being wirelessly connected to the WiFi router
		  for the primary LED lighting device to access internet;

the Zigbee modules from each of the primary LED lighting
		  device and the at least one secondary LED lighting device form a Zigbee
		  network;
